2011-05-10T07:09:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/ampire-co-ltd-april-sales-fall-10-22-table-8049-tt.html
AMPIRE CO LTD (8049)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 10.22% to NT$107,967,000 from NT$120,263,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            107,967          120,263    
YOY%             -10.22%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            390,896          484,892    
YOY%             -19.38% 
=================================================================
 